{"tid":1834342,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"用粘米粉整魚肉餅","createTime":"2020-01-22T10:42:28.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-23T09:39:37.000Z","uid":175025,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"beb7778fe81d6b6aaf4ceb31c6d0ff012c9fef91","tid":1834342,"uid":175025,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-22T10:42:28.000Z","msg":"話說媽媽叫我整魚肉餅，但我無記錯屋企一直都係無生粉既<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/think.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />而問佢，佢又話之前買左，好啦咁我咪整囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/ok.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />既然佢話有生粉<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/ok.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n到我加晒其他材料最後想搵包生粉撈埋一齊果時，屌，搵到果包係粘米粉黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我嬲到暴走左加左好L多既粘米粉落魚肉到，諗住鳩煮<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1SCuwcQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1SCuwcQ.jpg&h=f75801cc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />用手整成魚餅果時真係好L痴手呀<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/20.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/21.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n煮完之後又法國好似無事，未試食<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yeah.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JdgZTrF.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJdgZTrF.jpg&h=4ff92f56&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"89dfa98a9a4a05aa1f3a08e982a1a6018e117e74","tid":1834342,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-22T13:22:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e30d34fb9f5f1f09875cfab25b2511e2a1eed6a4","tid":1834342,"uid":340796,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-22T15:43:18.000Z","msg":"只係實D 囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1025